            {
                "comment": "Prof. Dan Negrut is the type of professor you want in all of your classes. Super funny guy, brings a lot of vitality to the zoom lectures. This class is one of my favorite classes at UW-Madison. The weekly programming assignments are a lot of work, but they are definitely doable.",
